'''腺苷受體'''(Adenosine receptor)，或稱為'''P1受體'''(P1 receptors)<ref name="pmid9133776">{{cite journal | vauthors = Fredholm BB, Abbracchio MP, Burnstock G, Dubyak GR, Harden TK, Jacobson KA, Schwabe U, Williams M | title = Towards a revised nomenclature for P1 and P2 receptors | journal = Trends Pharmacol. Sci. | volume = 18 | issue = 3 | pages = 79–82 | year = 1997 | pmid = 9133776 | doi = 10.1016/S0165-6147(96)01038-3 | pmc = 4460977 }}</ref>，是一類以[[腺苷|腺苷]]為內源性[[配體|配體]]的嘌呤能[[G蛋白偶聯受體|G蛋白偶聯受體]]。<ref name="pmid11734617">{{cite journal | vauthors = Fredholm BB, IJzerman AP, Jacobson KA, Klotz KN, Linden J | title = International Union of Pharmacology. XXV. Nomenclature and classification of adenosine receptors | journal = Pharmacol. Rev. | volume = 53 | issue = 4 | pages = 527–52 | year = 2001 | pmid = 11734617 | doi = | url = http://pharmrev.aspetjournals.org/cgi/content/abstract/53/4/527 }}</ref>人體中腺苷受體有四種已知類型：[[腺苷A1受體|A<sub>1</sub>]]、[[腺苷A2A受體|A<sub>2A</sub>]]、[[腺苷A2B受體|A<sub>2B</sub>]]和[[腺苷A3受體|A<sub>3</sub>]]；每個都由不同的[[基因|基因]]編碼。

腺苷受體因其[[腺苷受體拮抗劑|拮抗劑]][[咖啡因|咖啡因]]和[[茶鹼|茶鹼]]而聞名，它們對受體的作用產生了[[咖啡|咖啡]]、[[茶|茶]]和[[巧克力|巧克力]]的刺激提神作用。

